<title>ạ̉ṭlb wmạlysẖ gẖyrk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạṭlbk wmạlysẖ tạny gẖyrk ạnt fy ạlḥyạẗ
 ạʿysẖ lyk wạnt ạḥtyạjy ạw ạʿysẖ lyẗ tạny ạlḥyạẗ
 ʿlmny ạḥtạjk wtkwn ạnt ạḥtạjy ʿlmny ạḥtạjk wạkẖd mnk
 ạḥtyạjy yạ yswʿ ạnt ạḥtyạjy
 2- knt bʿyd qrbt
 bdmk bʿd mạ knt lwḥdy sẖryd kẖlyqẗ tạnyẗ tqdr
 ḥbk wbqyt fyk mkẖlwq jdyd
 ʿạysẖ bslạmk wsạkn fyk bạlrwḥ ʿạysẖ bslạmk yạlly sẖạftny
 mn ạljrwḥ yạ yswʿ ạnt slạmy
 3- kẖltny blạ lwm qdạmk bdmạk fy ạlṣlb wgẖnạk
 ạnạ myn ʿạysẖ bạkẖtyạrk
 wbdmk ạnạ ạʿysẖ fy smạk mdywn bḥyạty wbslmlk qlby wnfsy
 mdywn bḥyạty
 lyk yạ ạlhy mkẖlṣ nfsy yạyswʿ ạnt kẖlạṣy</lyrics>
</song>